Class UsernameMappingTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.timothy.tests.database.UsernameMappingTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MysqlUsernameMappingTest

    public class UsernameMappingTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes tests for a UsernameMapping in a MappingDatabase. The database must be completely empty after each setUp. The database will be modified. Do not run against an actual database.
